text: Walter Dean Bryan (born December 23, 1933) is a former American football player who played for the Baltimore Colts of the National Football League (NFL). He played college football at Tarleton State University and Texas Tech University. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:People from Olney, Texas Category:Players of American football from Texas Category:American football defensive backs Category:Tarleton State Texans football players Category:Texas Tech Red Raiders football players Category:Baltimore Colts players
